    "attributes": {
        "action": "Waive 2019/20 corporation tax & VAT for limited company directors",
        "additional_details": "The government have not provided any direct grants to the working small limited company director and these tax payers need help by waiving the corporation tax bills for the financial year 2019/2020 and to allow these small working limited company directors to retain the VAT that their small businesses have collected.\r\n\r\nWaive the corporation tax bill payable for 2019/20 tax year that is due and to waive the VAT collected by these hard working people who have been left without grants for nine months now.",
        "background": "To help the small limited company director who has received no meaningful grants from government.",
